Package com.hedera.hashgraph.sdk.token

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    TokenAssociateTransaction
    Associates the provided account with the provided tokens.
    TokenBurnTransaction
    Burns tokens from the Token's treasury Account.
    TokenCreateTransaction
    Create a new token.
    TokenDeleteTransaction
    Marks a token as deleted, though it will remain in the ledger.
    TokenDissociateTransaction
    Dissociates the provided account with the provided tokens.
    TokenFreezeTransaction
    Freezes transfers of the specified token for the account.
    TokenGrantKycTransaction
    Grants KYC to the account for the given token.
    TokenId  
    TokenInfo  
    TokenInfoQuery
    Gets information about Token instance
    TokenMintTransaction
    Mints tokens to the Token's treasury Account.
    TokenRevokeKycTransaction
    Revokes KYC to the account for the given token.
    TokenTransferTransaction
    Transfer tokens from some accounts to other accounts.
    TokenUnfreezeTransaction  
    TokenUpdateTransaction
    Updates an already created Token.
    TokenWipeTransaction
    Wipes the provided amount of tokens from the specified Account.
